                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18190707-27-off156 t18190707-27-cd157"></join>, one pewter quart pot, value 6 d.; one pint of rum, value 2 s., and 9 d. in copper monies numbered
            </rs>, the property of 
               <persName id="t18190707-27-victim304" type="victimName">
                  James Adamson 
                  Laird
               <interp inst="t18190707-27-victim304" type="surname" value="Laird"></interp>
